  "overview": "Based on 'Death of a Man in the Balkans (2012)', an original feature film of Miroslav Momcilovic, 'Sorria, Voc\u00ea Est\u00e1 Sendo Filmado' ('Smile, You're Being Filmed') tells the story of a suicide, in only one shot of 80 minutes, from the perspective of a web cam which only the suicidal knew was on, giving the viewer the feeling of watching everything from his window. \"From the screenplay to the shooting, we are doing a kind of reality cinema,\" sets this movie director Daniel Filho.",
